==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: generic name
<hw>ge*ner"ic name`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The name for a medication,
as used in the pharmacopoeia; it cannot be a trademark. The name is
typically given by the inventor or discoverer of the drug, but must be
approved by a national or international naming authority.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Generification</ent>⟦br⟧
